{"title":"Linfoma Hodgkin","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Paper. Linfoma Hodgkin-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Paper. Linfoma Hodgkin 2025","guid":"B9FyWDOp6kPQwAJ3Uanc2A","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## Visión general de\\Nla enfermedad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Linfoma de Hodgkin (LH): malignidad linfoide de células B poco común","guid":"69hFV_-IQpYwYxufZcaWSA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"- Afecta a 8570 nuevos pacientes anualmente (10% de todos los linfomas en Estados Unidos)","guid":"8_38-UbR_010qrCZn85Qmg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- Distribución bimodal: mayor incidencia en adultos jóvenes y en pacientes ≥55 años","guid":"oePq2o9gwZDbXoGaXrGLiA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"- Factores asociados:","guid":"L2YlWB1LikD2PE9fPuwNeQ","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"- Factores familiares (hermanos con riesgo 10 veces mayor)","guid":"ziQZDhubl1XCo6O2Az5NTw","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"- Exposiciones virales (virus Epstein-Barr)","guid":"iNGAB_XGwoQsZ7XMMMjRMQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"- Inmunosupresión (pacientes VIH positivos)","guid":"Tr3bcLzc1ZCvO8Ln6O1xmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"- Tasa de curación >80% en pacientes <60 años","guid":"f8HUUu8NpfJ7ZijcRQKTtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"## Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"- Presentación común: linfadenopatía supradiafragmática","guid":"WkzhuL915lUep9NHrR8Vgg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"- Ganglios cervicales, mediastínicos anteriores, supraclaviculares y axilares","guid":"J2_gA_4yoBqukChdcWxg_Q","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"- Áreas inguinales menos frecuentemente afectadas","guid":"kFsxvgpU2br1dQ1xbXOHvg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"- Un tercio presenta síntomas sistémicos (fiebre, sudores nocturnos, pérdida de peso)","guid":"IT5Yyo4IKROKCTMs4abU1Q","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"- Prurito crónico común","guid":"809ftAwuMuES-IsyRZFvJw","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"- Diagnóstico solo por biopsia (no PAAF o biopsia con aguja gruesa)","guid":"RyKDvJSWy1TCUQNyVvRLpQ","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"10","text":"- Identificación de célula maligna de Reed-Sternberg necesaria","guid":"4y6lP3s3S_zjNCzazwbvCg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"10","text":"### Entidades de\\Nenfermedad","guid":"pyGHA0qPndb3MBgR-KjqfQ","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"1. **Linfoma de\\NHodgkin clásico**","guid":"IAp9xHPSQIbX9ArWf4Rgkw","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"- Subtipos:","guid":"79aD-jJuJS6SOYIvLqQfSg","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"- Esclerosis nodular (más común)","guid":"KgbOWLsmvhxS6rKCS2FqOQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"- Celularidad mixta","guid":"IJESn7zkeOvXNeWFuhL2Sw","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"- Depleción linfocítica","guid":"0vtjGmZaIQaqsX3zHtxPXA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"- Rico en linfocitos","guid":"wS0863iXqrFjo2b9plWjgw","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"19","text":"- Sobreexpresión de ligandos PD-1 en células Reed-Sternberg","guid":"EObi3_O36AntFLcmqEPMug","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"19","text":"- Subtipos genómicos: clúster H1 (68%) y H2 (32%)","guid":"GJ5rCDq_k6iA5ZM_NBf2SA","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"18","text":"2. **Linfoma de Hodgkin\\Npredominante en linfocitos\\Nnodulares**","guid":"zYLqcoTVp75w7bAjog-2zQ","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"- Propuesta reciente: \"Linfoma de células B predominante en linfocitos nodulares\"","guid":"JGGIHnMYVsdR4l6Z24sV5Q","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"- Sin células Reed-Sternberg típicas","guid":"AeII4ubgDZMyF4Cl6wZNzg","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"- Células neoplásicas L&H (linfocíticas e histiocíticas)","guid":"pW0AG7c60rEOQS3kyANwIQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"- CD20+ y generalmente CD30-","guid":"h3otGYIDyopvqUNLQ5yi2Q","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"27","text":"- Más frecuente en hombres","guid":"_7j_Zny-V3NBiqRvcjXBEg","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"27","text":"- Curso indolente con recurrencias tardías","guid":"CmtbDdS6INwery1nW6P32Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"## Estratificación\\Nde riesgo","guid":"Nk_RopqA-XQd8vGbAcej1Q","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"- Evaluación precisa del estadio crítica para selección de terapia","guid":"gOSUCaexLBDvh5ey7YqgmQ","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"- PET con FDG: herramienta importante en estadificación","guid":"OHlUxRy8Iz3FCxdfsiek4Q","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"- Factores pronósticos\\Npara estadio temprano:","guid":"LEWHi5nMZR5w3xVbgYVHJg","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"- Masa mediastínica grande","guid":"lI9PCw0RmHSBiB5UG8Ze1g","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"- VHS elevada","guid":"vVh_094eIU4nuKsGcKXqkg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"- Afectación de múltiples sitios ganglionares","guid":"qQax8CgBSawStISMoE4lag","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"- Compromiso extraganglionar","guid":"zliEpoahjbvDGuJL_BUkwg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"37","text":"- Edad ≥50 años","guid":"zXjGabSTsRKPSX4Gn2vFrA","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"37","text":"- Enfermedad esplénica masiva","guid":"96Pq49HJpJt3N6ygbJtgDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"34","text":"- Sistema de puntuación\\Npronóstica para LH avanzado:","guid":"JOtXxKg4QVSGE_2z6BjCQQ","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"- 7 variables: edad ≥45 años, estadio IV, sexo masculino, leucocitos ≥15, 000/μL,\\Nlinfocitos <600/μL, albúmina <4.0 g/dL, hemoglobina <10.5 g/dL","guid":"ddt_oxg44WtM1G2y7smKqw","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"34","text":"- Volumen tumoral metabólico (MTV) en PET inicial: importante factor predictivo","guid":"3X6ItRQXLwaofwo10VM_Ag","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"## Terapia inicial\\Nadaptada al riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"- Factores\\Ndeterminantes:","guid":"A0CLJEM8yxcF_DSTi8Zxhw","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"- Histología (LH clásico o predominante en linfocitos nodulares)","guid":"GzchDglvebaFt9VxAskpnw","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"- Estadio anatómico (limitado o avanzado)","guid":"ocpWyUOgs6oIILbuup1QDg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"- Presencia de factores pronósticos desfavorables","guid":"h0rmRObNLRiZwNpEojahag","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"- Síntomas constitucionales","guid":"4hQjOZcy4176x2s253kDbg","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"48","text":"- Enfermedad voluminosa (>10 cm)","guid":"ISZHe8WZwM0sMdZHvVvMug","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"47","text":"- PET con FDG: rol prominente en decisiones terapéuticas","guid":"QAfFSyxN3YqTmWnqPhvfxg","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"0","text":"### Enfoque terapéutico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"1. **Estadio temprano\\Nfavorable**","guid":"N2ELBUiuzzx6bP2zjk-16A","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- Quimioterapia de corta duración + radioterapia de campo involucrado (IFRT)","guid":"nTleBd1PZarBiG71n_l4Zg","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"- 2 ciclos ABVD + 20Gy IFRT: estándar actual","guid":"ekooza47miZmGaHhDUO9pA","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"2. **Estadio temprano\\Ndesfavorable**","guid":"ZEBm5aeUj25xqebOcf2fYQ","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"- 4 ciclos de quimioterapia combinada + IFRT","guid":"KpZ8JoJAv_AXvNiFhCoqhQ","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"- ABVD por 4 ciclos + 30Gy IFRT: estándar","guid":"4zN9fjrouLkLx6mzt3EQXw","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"- Nuevos agentes (brentuximab vedotin, anti-PD-1) muestran resultados excelentes","guid":"BtKhv2MWD_OzP_5toM2PGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"55","text":"3. **Tratamiento\\Nadaptado a respuesta**","guid":"QUrhv1IS6Ndj1fjYL0fxXw","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"- PET negativo después de 2-3 ciclos: puede omitirse radioterapia","guid":"OLaQl9ulR5XwV0rEeWugyA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"- Estudios RAPID y H10: control de enfermedad ligeramente inferior sin radioterapia","guid":"Ac8IXsRmYA3lIywu3pVimA","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"55","text":"4. **Enfermedad avanzada\\N(estadios IIB-IV)**","guid":"1GPszhCGCt_AqjCrbYAuSQ","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"- Debate: quimioterapia moderada (ABVD) vs. intensiva (BEACOPP escalado)","guid":"v__JVylVn30EkLfMriA7qA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"- Nuevos enfoques:","guid":"aW1q90we6GjY3WJfYlpdTw","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"- BV-AVD: superior a ABVD (mejora SLP y SG)","guid":"dxSq_C-P4EKIDVmZ3tLvug","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"- BrECADD: mejor tolerado y más efectivo que BEACOPP escalado","guid":"PA-n84SQ5oJ-yaMofcIL2w","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"- N-AVD: mejor SLP que BV-AVD en seguimiento a 1 año","guid":"fA4UBo-v_dN20Ej4l-0LHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"66","text":"- Pacientes ancianos: combinaciones con brentuximab vedotin o nivolumab","guid":"4odpuMw-FEnlHVUJyQJ3Lg","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"55","text":"5. **Linfoma predominante en\\Nlinfocitos nodulares**","guid":"aHTB6moGdlmADkp5fri_ig","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"- Estadio IA favorable: escisión ganglionar + \"observar y esperar\" o IFRT","guid":"fKVHl12ytuyoQZhG3sCdsg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"- Estadio avanzado: quimioterapia combinada + rituximab","guid":"gvWdgGYgPH4oEfkP9awdcA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"0","text":"## Manejo de enfermedad\\Nrecaída/refractaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"1. **Enfermedad primaria refractaria**","guid":"9UQungoblKIYzX48oDTs1g","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"- Quimioterapia a altas dosis (HDCT) + trasplante autólogo de células madre (ASCT)","guid":"ywaPJlGGNDwpQ3x9pOyv3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"2. **Enfermedad recaída**","guid":"pVmv7h1aR4-o9uGXFqIAnQ","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"- Quimioterapia de rescate + ASCT","guid":"3P0I-yWHQa2T9vhZHyQKJA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"- Adición de brentuximab vedotin o anti-PD-1: mejora tasas de respuesta completa","guid":"ajbHZN1a37zVX0Q79C6a6g","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"- Consolidación post-trasplante con brentuximab vedotin: beneficio en pacientes de alto riesgo","guid":"0yAomedNVv9GK9OJCXzJUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"76","text":"3. **Opciones terapéuticas tras recaída\\Ndespués de HDCT y ASCT**","guid":"v09ouANS-CL_EGJB7rSZmA","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"- Brentuximab vedotin: actividad clínica significativa","guid":"dhpdCQBAtum-CKc3bh10ig","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"- Bloqueo PD-1 (pembrolizumab): superior a brentuximab vedotin","guid":"IABLr-VPkbZXqHmQBDFp3w","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"- Enfoques\\Nprometedores:","guid":"5MILAswUNJxdDowCWenXGA","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"- Estrategias combinadas","guid":"o0Eik-QPD59b9Aj06-ZhVQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"- Terapia con células CAR-T","guid":"bqcCpavBEq3lymck7c06GQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"- Nuevos conjugados anticuerpo-fármaco","guid":"xxXLvW1jTVkg9_j8Nm0r-w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"## Resumen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"- Manejo óptimo requiere diagnóstico preciso y estadificación cuidadosa","guid":"C4--PbgDuNOKGviWkDb75g","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"- Terapia adaptada al riesgo aumenta probabilidad de curación y limita toxicidad","guid":"PiW8yKzoUHBzcY70u_6gaA","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"- Dirección futura: incorporar agentes novedosos y utilizar imágenes y\\Nensayos moleculares para minimizar tratamiento necesario","guid":"nPVmH5d_HQTyyLmEjr3OeA","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":93,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"Paper. Linfoma Hodgkin-2025-1","id":"map_1079","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Paper. Linfoma Hodgkin-2025-1"}